        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Border Construction Materials Transfer Act of 2022 </b></p> <p>This bill requires the federal government to transfer, without reimbursement, materials purchased for the construction of roadways or barriers along the U.S.-Mexico border and located in the states of Texas, Arizona, New Mexico, or California to the governments of those states.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
